---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contractor Software Hub" description="Independent, honest reviews of contractor software. No vendor copy. No padding. Just honest calls on what each tool costs, what it gets right, and who it's wrong for.">

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     HERO
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="relative bg-[#0f172a] text-white overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Dot-grid background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 26px 26px;"></div>
  <!-- Subtle bottom vignette -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-32 pointer-events-none" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(15,23,42,0.6));"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-20 sm:py-28">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- Left: Headline -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <!-- Eyebrow pill -->
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#E07A3A]/15 border border-[#E07A3A]/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 mb-7">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-[#E07A3A] rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
          <span class="text-[#E07A3A] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest">Independent Software Reviews for Contractors</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-[3.5rem] font-bold leading-[1.1] mb-6" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; color: white;">
          Most contractor software<br>
          reviews are useless.<br>
          <span style="color: #E07A3A;">These aren't.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-lg">
          No vendor copy. No padding. Honest calls on what each tool costs, what it gets right, and who it's wrong for — for contractors running 1–50 people.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="#by-trade" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-[#E07A3A] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-[#C05E20] transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg">
            Browse by Trade →
          </a>
          <a href="#top-picks" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-white/10 border border-white/20 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-200">
            See Top Reviews
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Stat strip -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 mt-10 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
          <div>
            <p class="text-2xl font-black text-white" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;">23+</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Reviews & Guides</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-2xl font-black text-white" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;">6</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Trades Covered</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-2xl font-black text-white" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;">100%</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Independent</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Featured Top Pick card -->
      <div class="hidden lg:block lg:col-span-5">
        <div class="bg-white/[0.05] backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-2xl">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-5">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-[#E07A3A]/20 border border-[#E07A3A]/40 text-[#E07A3A] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
              <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
              Our Top Pick
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#e0f2fe] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-black text-[#0369a1] shrink-0">J</div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-white text-xl" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;">Jobber</p>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Field Service Software · From $49/mo</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-5">Best all-around for contractors running 1–25 employees. Scheduling, invoicing, and client communication in one clean package.</p>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mb-5">
            <span class="text-xs bg-white/10 text-gray-300 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">Scheduling</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-white/10 text-gray-300 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">Invoicing</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-white/10 text-gray-300 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">Client CRM</span>
            <span class="text-xs bg-white/10 text-gray-300 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md">Mobile App</span>
          </div>

          <a href="/blog/jobber-review/" class="block w-full text-center py-3 bg-[#E07A3A] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-[#C05E20] transition-all text-sm">
            Read the Full Review →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     BY TRADE  — Primary Discovery Path
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="by-trade" class="py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">

    <div class="flex items-end gap-4 mb-10">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-1" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;">Find Software for Your Trade</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500">Pick your trade for a guide built around how you actually work.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">

      <!-- HVAC — blue -->
      <a href="/blog/hvac-software/" class="group relative bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg hover:border-[#E07A3A] transition-all duration-200">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-[#3B82F6]"></div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🔧</div>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1C2B4B] mb-1" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;">HVAC</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">7 options reviewed</p>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#E07A3A] group-hover:underline">View Guide →</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Plumbing — cyan -->
      <a href="/blog/plumbing-software/" class="group relative bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg hover:border-[#E07A3A] transition-all duration-200">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-[#06B6D4]"></div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🔩</div>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1C2B4B] mb-1" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;">Plumbing</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">5 options reviewed</p>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#E07A3A] group-hover:underline">View Guide →</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Roofing — amber -->
      <a href="/blog/roofing-software/" class="group relative bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg hover:border-[#E07A3A] transition-all duration-200">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-[#F59E0B]"></div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🏠</div>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1C2B4B] mb-1" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;">Roofing</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">5 options reviewed</p>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#E07A3A] group-hover:underline">View Guide →</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Landscaping — green -->
      <a href="/blog/landscaping-software/" class="group relative bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg hover:border-[#E07A3A] transition-all duration-200">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-[#22C55E]"></div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🌿</div>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1C2B4B] mb-1" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;">Landscaping</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">6 options reviewed</p>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#E07A3A] group-hover:underline">View Guide →</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Pest Control — yellow -->
      <a href="/blog/pest-control-software/" class="group relative bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg hover:border-[#E07A3A] transition-all duration-200">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-[#EAB308]"></div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🐛</div>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1C2B4B] mb-1" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;">Pest Control</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">5 options reviewed</p>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#E07A3A] group-hover:underline">View Guide →</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- Painting — purple -->
      <a href="/blog/best-software-painting-contractors/" class="group relative bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg hover:border-[#E07A3A] transition-all duration-200">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-[#A855F7]"></div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🎨</div>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1C2B4B] mb-1" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;">Painting</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">5 options reviewed</p>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#E07A3A] group-hover:underline">View Guide →</span>
        </div>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     TOP PICKS
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="top-picks" class="bg-[#F5F7FA] border-y border-gray-200 py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">

    <div class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-1" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;">Most-Read Reviews</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500">The tools contractors look up most. Each review aggregates real contractor feedback, pricing details, and hands-on testing.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

      <!-- Jobber — Top Pick (orange border) -->
      <a href="/blog/jobber-review/" class="group bg-white border-2 border-[#E07A3A] rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-[#E07A3A]"></div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#e0f2fe] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black text-[#0369a1] shrink-0">J</div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-lg text-[#1C2B4B] leading-tight">Jobber</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">From $49/mo</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mb-3">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs bg-[#FFF3E8] text-[#E07A3A] border border-[#E07A3A]/30 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full font-semibold">⭐ Top Pick</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full">1–25 techs</span>
        </div>

        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4 flex-1">Best all-around field service software for small contractors. Scheduling, invoicing, and client comms in one clean package with a short learning curve.</p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 mb-5">
          <span class="text-[11px] bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Scheduling</span>
          <span class="text-[11px] bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Invoicing</span>
          <span class="text-[11px] bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Client CRM</span>
        </div>

        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#E07A3A] group-hover:underline">Read Full Review →</span>
      </a>

      <!-- Housecall Pro -->
      <a href="/blog/housecall-pro-review/" class="group bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-[#1C2B4B] hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#fce7f3] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black text-[#be185d] shrink-0">H</div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-lg text-[#1C2B4B] leading-tight">Housecall Pro</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">From $65/mo</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mb-3">
          <span class="text-xs bg-[#1C2B4B] text-white px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full font-semibold">Strong Pick</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full">1–20 techs</span>
        </div>

        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4 flex-1">Best mobile app in the field service category. Built-in review requests on most plans — keeps your Google ratings growing without extra effort.</p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 mb-5">
          <span class="text-[11px] bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Mobile App</span>
          <span class="text-[11px] bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Review Requests</span>
          <span class="text-[11px] bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Dispatch</span>
        </div>

        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#1C2B4B] group-hover:underline">Read Full Review →</span>
      </a>

      <!-- ServiceTitan -->
      <a href="/blog/servicetitan-review/" class="group bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-[#1C2B4B] hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#e2e8f0] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-black text-[#475569] shrink-0">ST</div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-lg text-[#1C2B4B] leading-tight">ServiceTitan</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">From $398/mo</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mb-3">
          <span class="text-xs bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full font-semibold">Specialist</span>
          <span class="text-xs bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full">10+ techs</span>
        </div>

        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4 flex-1">Enterprise-grade for contractors doing $1M+ in revenue. Best reporting and automation — but the price and learning curve are real.</p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 mb-5">
          <span class="text-[11px] bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Enterprise</span>
          <span class="text-[11px] bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Reporting</span>
          <span class="text-[11px] bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Automation</span>
        </div>

        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#1C2B4B] group-hover:underline">Read Full Review →</span>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     HEAD-TO-HEAD COMPARISONS
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">

    <div class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-1" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;">Head-to-Head Comparisons</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500">Stuck choosing between two tools? These cut straight to the verdict.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">

      <a href="/blog/jobber-vs-housecall-pro/" class="group flex items-center gap-4 p-5 bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl hover:border-[#E07A3A] hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 shrink-0">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#e0f2fe] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-black text-[#0369a1]">J</div>
          <span class="text-gray-300 font-bold text-xs">vs</span>
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#fce7f3] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-black text-[#be185d]">H</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
          <p class="font-semibold text-[#1C2B4B] group-hover:text-[#E07A3A] transition-colors text-sm">Jobber vs Housecall Pro</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-0.5">Best overall vs best mobile app</p>
        </div>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-300 group-hover:text-[#E07A3A] shrink-0 transition-colors" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/servicetitan-vs-jobber/" class="group flex items-center gap-4 p-5 bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl hover:border-[#E07A3A] hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 shrink-0">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#e2e8f0] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-black text-[#475569]">ST</div>
          <span class="text-gray-300 font-bold text-xs">vs</span>
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#e0f2fe] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-black text-[#0369a1]">J</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
          <p class="font-semibold text-[#1C2B4B] group-hover:text-[#E07A3A] transition-colors text-sm">ServiceTitan vs Jobber</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-0.5">Enterprise scale vs small team</p>
        </div>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-300 group-hover:text-[#E07A3A] shrink-0 transition-colors" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>

      <a href="/blog/housecall-pro-vs-fieldedge/" class="group flex items-center gap-4 p-5 bg-white border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-xl hover:border-[#E07A3A] hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 shrink-0">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#fce7f3] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-black text-[#be185d]">H</div>
          <span class="text-gray-300 font-bold text-xs">vs</span>
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#fef3c7] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-black text-[#92400e]">FE</div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
          <p class="font-semibold text-[#1C2B4B] group-hover:text-[#E07A3A] transition-colors text-sm">HCP vs FieldEdge</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-0.5">Easy setup vs QuickBooks depth</p>
        </div>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-300 group-hover:text-[#E07A3A] shrink-0 transition-colors" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     BY CATEGORY
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="bg-[#F5F7FA] border-y border-gray-200 py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">

    <div class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-1" style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;">Browse by Business Function</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500">Looking to improve a specific part of your operation?</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4">

      <a href="/blog/best-estimating-software-small-contractors/" class="group flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl hover:border-[#E07A3A] hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-200">
